====關於曲目====
[[Image:SituationsEP.jpg|150px]]
第一首歌〈Situations〉是首張專輯《{{link-en|Dying Is Your Latest Fashion|Dying Is Your Latest Fashion}}》中的第二首單曲，<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.cduniverse.com/productinfo.asp?pid=7267029&style=music&fulldesc=T| title=Dying Is Your Latest Fashion on CD Universe}}</ref>單曲發行於2007年11月20日。這首歌的內容可以從音樂錄影帶中得知，是羅尼·拉德克的第一人稱視角。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=USriZAMR2nA|title=Official Situations music video|access-date=2014-04-29|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227224614/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=USriZAMR2nA|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第二首歌〈Make Up〉是從樣本專輯Escape the Fate重新錄製，同時也是《{{link-en|Dying Is Your Latest Fashion|Dying Is Your Latest Fashion}}》日本版的附贈歌曲。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/dying-is-your-latest-fashion-mw0000444242| title=Dying Is Your Latest Fashion on Allmusic| access-date=2014-04-29| archive-date=2020-09-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911015224/https://www.allmusic.com/album/dying-is-your-latest-fashion-mw0000444242| dead-url=no}}</ref>

第三個軌道則是〈''Situations''〉的官方音樂錄影帶。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/archive_2796 |title=archive |access-date=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202235839/http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/archive_2796 |archive-date=2014-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

