===歌曲資訊===
樂團為歌曲〈Not Good Enough for Truth in Cliché〉製作音樂錄影帶，以樂團在內華達州沙漠一同表演為特色。蔗部錄影帶由J. Reyes製作。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YR5-FFJLWPw| title=''Youtube'' Not Good Enough for Truth in Cliche (Demo)| publisher=youtube| year=2005| accessdate=2008-03-11| archive-date=2018-10-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181017025512/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YR5-FFJLWPw| dead-url=no}}</ref>

* 〈Not Good Enough for Truth in Cliché〉是從專輯《{{link-en|Dying Is Your Latest Fashion|Dying Is Your Latest Fashion}}》重新錄製。同時也是此張專輯中首張發行單曲。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/dying-is-your-latest-fashion-r854464/review| title=List of songs on the album Dying Is Your Latest Fashion| publisher=allmusic| date=2006-09-26| accessdate=2012-03-11| archive-date=2019-12-10| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210165109/http://www.allmusic.com/album/dying-is-your-latest-fashion-r854464/review| dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 〈Make Up〉被重新錄製並作為附贈歌曲發行於《{{link-en|Dying Is Your Latest Fashion|Dying Is Your Latest Fashion}}》日本版。也是《[[Situations_EP|Situations EP]]》中的歌曲。
* 〈Chariot of Fire〉以〈When I Go Out, I Want to Go Out On a Chariot of Fire〉之名被重新錄製並發行於首張全長專輯《Dying Is Your Latest Fashion》。
* 〈I Can Swing a Mic Like Nobody's Business〉重新命名為〈{{link-en|There's No Sympathy for the Dead|There's No Sympathy for the Dead}}〉，並重新錄製發行於2006年的首張迷你專輯《There's No Sympathy for the Dead》以及首張全長專輯《Dying Is Your Latest Fashion》。
* 〈As I'm Falling Down〉被重新錄製為〈As You're Falling Down〉，並包含於迷你專輯《There's No Sympathy for the Dead》與《Situations》。
* 〈The Structure Falls〉是唯一沒有被重新錄製的；它只有樣本而已。

